From 9350e9665972f827466a56d0d9b036071c0f197c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kol Crooks <kol.crooks@datadoghq.com>
Date: Tue, 5 May 2026 09:58:26 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Phase 8: Storyboard sub-mode (chapter dependency graph)

Adds a fourth sub-mode to the PR editor that visualises the
Phase-7 chapter graph using `Chapter.dependsOn[]`. Pure SVG/DOM
inside the existing EditorPane (no React webview); tier-by-
dependency-depth layout with single-bend Manhattan edge routing
and stagger ports for nodes with multiple incoming/outgoing
edges. Hover-to-spotlight dims unrelated nodes/edges; clicking
a node populates a detail rail with the chapter's title,
summary, bullets, and clickable upstream/downstream
connections.
